BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 591.00 Tm (Okay everyone, let's get started. Welcome to this session on JDBC. Now, JDBC stands for Java) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 575.80 Tm (Database Connectivity, and that is exactly what it does - it is the bridge that connects your Java) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 560.60 Tm (program to a database.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 540.40 Tm (Let me start with a question for you to think about. In all the Java programs you have written so) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 525.20 Tm (far, where does your data live? It lives in variables, in objects, in an ArrayList - in other words, it) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 510.00 Tm (lives in the computer's memory. And here is the problem with memory: the moment your program) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 494.80 Tm (stops, all of that memory is wiped clean. Everything is gone.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 474.60 Tm (So today we solve that problem permanently. We are going to learn how Java saves data into a) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 459.40 Tm (real database, so that even if the program closes, even if the computer restarts, the data is still) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 444.20 Tm (safely there when you come back.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 424.00 Tm (And one more thing before we dive in - I know some of you are excited to learn Spring and) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 408.80 Tm (Hibernate later. Here is the good news: JDBC is the foundation that all of those are built on top of.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 393.60 Tm (So when you understand JDBC, those advanced tools will never feel like magic. You will know) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 378.40 Tm (exactly what is happening underneath.) Tj ET
0.040 0.520 1.000 rg 58.00 363.20 3.00 249.80 re f
