BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 590.70 Tm (database company gives us. Two - there are four driver types, and Type four, the pure Java one,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 575.50 Tm (is the one we always use. Three - the four characters: DriverManager opens the door, Connection) Tj ET
